---
import InfoPageLayout from "../layouts/InfoPageLayout.astro";
import MaxWidthWrapper from "../components/MaxWidthWrapper.astro";
---

<InfoPageLayout pageTitle="About iTechedThat">
  <section class="min-h-[85vh] py-12">
    <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-screen-xl py-2.5 md:px-20">
      <a
        href="/"
        class="group relative inline-flex h-12 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-md bg-neutral-950 font-medium text-neutral-200"
      >
        <div class="ml-1 transition group-hover:-translate-x-1">
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="16"
            height="16"
            fill="currentColor"
            class="bi bi-arrow-left"
            viewBox="0 0 16 16"
          >
            <path
              fill-rule="evenodd"
              d="M15 8a.5.5 0 0 0-.5-.5H2.707l3.147-3.146a.5.5 0 1 0-.708-.708l-4 4a.5.5 0 0 0 0 .708l4 4a.5.5 0 0 0 .708-.708L2.707 8.5H14.5A.5.5 0 0 0 15 8"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <span class="text-2xl">Back it Up</span></a
      >
    </div>
    <MaxWidthWrapper>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 grid-col-1">
        <div>
          <div class="pb-12 md:flex md:flex-col">
            <h2 class="text-neutral-200 text-4xl inline-block font-bold">
              About
            </h2>
            <span
              class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-600 to-pink-600"
            >
              iTechedThat
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
            <p class="text-neutral-300 font-semibold text-xl">
              Hi I&#39;m Yuukiburry. When I went to locals, I was your average
              1-2er. I needed a lot of help. I looked for any type of video,
              Google Doc, wiki or Reddit post that could take me to the next
              level. I was done being mediocre. I never did stop being mediocre
              but I&#39;ve been able to complile a bunch of cool resources along
              the way and want to share them with you.
            </p>
            <p class="text-neutral-300 font-semibold text-xl">
              These days it&#39;s hard to find resources if you forget to
              bookmark it, or if you&#39;re Twitter feed refreshes. Feel free to
              contribute resources that you think would be helpful.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </MaxWidthWrapper>
  </section>
</InfoPageLayout>
